본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap (analytical + biomarker meta-platform). hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 mass spec proteomics (질량분석 + 단백체학 + 다중-plex affinity proteomics) 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + analytical platform + biomarker discovery falsifier inventory.

(Distinct from `.roadmap.disease_liquid_biopsy` (DNA-RNA 중심) + `.roadmap.disease_theranostic` (image): mass spec proteomics = 단백질-수준 biomarker + drug-target engagement + post-translational modification + plasma proteomics + tissue proteomics. 2018+ Olink (PEA proximity extension assay) + Somascan (SOMAmer aptamer) → high-plex 5,000+ protein simultaneous detection. 양자-VQE 의 fit: peptide sequence + cross-linking + structural mass-spec 양자 적용.)

scope:
- bottom-up proteomics (trypsin digest + LC-MS/MS)
- top-down proteomics (intact protein)
- targeted MS (multiple reaction monitoring MRM + parallel reaction monitoring PRM)
- DIA (data-independent acquisition) + DDA (data-dependent)
- post-translational modification (PTM) — phosphorylation + glycosylation + acetylation
- plasma proteomics (Olink + Somascan + Seer Proteograph + Mass Spec)
- single-cell proteomics (scProteomics — emerging)
- HDX-MS (hydrogen-deuterium exchange — drug binding 보고)
- cross-linking MS (XL-MS — protein-protein interaction)
- thermal proteome profiling (TPP — drug-target engagement)
- ion mobility (IMS-MS — TIMS Bruker + cyclic IMS Waters + structures-for-lossless ion manipulations SLIM)
- imaging MS (MALDI Imaging + DESI — tissue spatial)
- proteogenomics (전사 + 단백 통합)
- 양자-VQE peptide structure prediction
- biomarker discovery + validation
- companion diagnostic protein-level (vs DNA)
- circulating biomarker (NfL + plasma p-tau217 + Olink + Somascan)

