## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **Olink Explore HT 2023 5,400-plex** = PEA dual-antibody + DNA-barcode 가 1,500→5,400 protein 동시 측정 (single 6μL plasma). Olink Insight (2024) 가 clinical translation. 양자-VQE 의 dual-Ab proximity binding pocket 적용.
2. **SomaScan v4.1 7,000-plex** = SOMAmer slow-off-rate aptamer. Olink (PEA) 와 head-to-head 비교 시 protein coverage overlap ~50%, 각자 unique protein 가 큼. 보완적 사용.
3. **Seer Proteograph 2024** = nano-particle enrichment + LC-MS 가 plasma dynamic range (10^11) 문제 해결. proteoform-level resolution 가 Olink/SomaScan 의 epitope-restricted limitation 보완.
4. **timsTOF Pro 2 + Astral + ZenoTOF 7600 2022-2024** = 차세대 mass analyzer 폭발. TIMS-PASEF (Bruker) + Astral (Thermo) + Zeno (SCIEX) 가 single-cell proteomics + DIA throughput 10× 향상.
5. **plasma p-tau217 Lumipulse 2024 first FDA Alzheimer 진단** = first FDA blood-based AD diagnostic (Aducanumab + Lecanemab biomarker). cross-`.roadmap.disease_dementia_specific` direct cross-link.
6. **NfL Quanterix Simoa** = single-molecule array. ALS + dementia + MS biomarker. tofersen (SOD1 ALS 2023) + Aducanumab/Lecanemab (Alzheimer) 의 surrogate endpoint. cross-`.roadmap.disease_inherited_adult` + `.roadmap.disease_dementia_specific`.
7. **HDX-MS (Waters Synapt XS + Bruker Apex Auto) + TPP (Cellzome + Pelago)** = drug-target engagement 의 orthogonal validation. SPR + ITC 외 in-cell engagement. quantum-VQE 의 binding pocket 가 HDX 와 cross-validation.
8. **XL-MS (DSSO + DSBU) + xQuest** = protein-protein interaction interface mapping. cryo-EM 보완 (low-resolution flexible region). PPI drug discovery (cross-`.roadmap.disease_AI_drug_discovery`).
9. **HUPO + Human Protein Atlas + ProteomicsDB + PeptideAtlas** = public proteomics atlas — 21,000+ protein 카탈로그. AI/quantum 학습 데이터 backbone.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, analytical platform 의미 한정. plasma p-tau217 + NfL 만 FDA-cleared clinical biomarker.

